      <minor />
      <comment>/* Gameplay */ not a [[pull quote]] (per [[WP:MOS]])</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox game
|title= Bunnies &amp; Burrows
|image= [[Image:bunnies and burrows.jpg|200px]]
