      <comment>/* Early history */ clarified some dates. supplied required citation</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox company
| name             = Bacardi &amp; Company Limited
| logo             = [[Image:Bacardi Logo.svg|The Bacardi logo]]
