      <text xml:space="preserve">'''Blackridge''' is a community in eastern [[Allegheny County, Pennsylvania|Allegheny County]] and is a suburb of [[Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania]]. This community consists of about 650 private homes built in 1920-1949, Blackridge Estates was and remains one of the area's largest residential communities. 

Blackridge lies in the municipalities of [[Wilkinsburg, Pennsylvania|Wilkinsburg]], [[Penn Hills, Pennsylvania|Penn Hills]] and [[Churchill, Pennsylvania|Churchill]]. It maintains a Civic Association and a private park and swim club for residents.


