      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Infobox television
| show_name          = Bagpuss
| image              = [[Image:Bagpuss.jpg|200px]]
| caption            = The original Bagpuss as seen in the series
| format             = [[Children's television]]
| runtime            = 
| creator            = [[Peter Firmin]] and [[Oliver Postgate]]
| starring           = 
| narrated           = [[Oliver Postgate]]
| country      = UK
| network      = [[BBC]]&lt;!--Only show the original network -- see template documentation--&gt;
| first_aired  = 12 February 1974
| last_aired   = 7 May 1974
| num_episodes = 13
