*&quot;Benjamin David Santer.&quot; Marquis Who's Who TM. Marquis Who's Who, 2009. Reproduced in Biography Resource Center. [[Farmington Hills, Michigan]]: [[Gale (Cengage)|Gale]], 2009. http://galenet.galegroup.com/servlet/BioRC Document Number: K2017060303. Fee. Accessed 2009-10-22 via [[Fairfax County Public Library]].

